name: Purple MAC
description: Purple Mac is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between MAC and Purple Punch. Bred by Purple City Genetics, Purple Mac is 21% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Leafly customers tell us Purple Mac effects make them feel euphoric, hungry, and creative. Medical marijuana patients often choose Purple Mac when dealing with symptoms associated with pain, stress, and insomnia. The dominant terpene of this cannabis strain is limonene. Purple Mac features an aroma and flavor profile that is floral, sweet, and has notes of diesel.
